It all started with the 17 "Origins," whose powers were passed down to individuals who still exist around the world today. A man carrying a coffin and a girl with the eyes of a beast appear in a town. The girl was once cursed by a witch and now searches for her in order to undo the curse. Is the witch who appears before them the quarry they've been searching for? And how can the curse be undone? This quest for revenge against an evil witch begins rolling when the beast captures the witch. This magnificent and intense dark fantasy begins now!
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonalds best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maous plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emis child! (Source: Crunchyroll)
Comedy, Drama, Romance, Slice of Life

"What am I doing?" Yuuhi Nagi's high school life is already halfway over, but he still doesn't have any dreams, ambitions, or even friends in his class! Every day is boring, until he's suddenly in danger of getting held back! A bittersweet high school drama made up of 4 potential grade repeaters with the worst grades in the class and 1 student acting as their teacher!
(Source: Pocket Comics)

A story about a demon who falls in love with an exorcist. While snow was falling on a holy night, a demon with the looks of a young girl traveled into the village and watched the warm people inside their homes. The demon was surprised when an exorcist spoke to the demon despite the hatred between the two species; immediately the demon fell in love with the exorcist. Includes 7 bonus chapters.
